{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"735efaf10e","title":"右派言论——“阶级分析方法已经过时”","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4cb51b1e48","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"735efaf10e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"54821d2745","name":"岳安良"},{"id":"6c72d91291","name":"河南农学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8276e55d94","type":"title","text":"右派言论——“阶级分析方法已经过时”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"735efaf10e"},{"id":"8ce03d2342","type":"authors","text":"河南农学院岳安良","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"735efaf10e"},{"id":"c2e406fb96","type":"paragraph","text":"（岳安良：河南农学院58级学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"735efaf10e"},{"id":"046ca57c07","type":"paragraph","text":"阶级分析方法已经过时，应按物质分配，将社会成员分为四个集团：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"735efaf10e"},{"id":"41d3bebf03","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）工人集团；","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"735efaf10e"},{"id":"9ce76d93b2","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）农民集团；","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"735efaf10e"},{"id":"cee412c501","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）知识分子集团；","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"735efaf10e"},{"id":"81533e50b9","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）国家干部集团。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"735efaf10e"},{"id":"d110cf9d44","type":"paragraph","text":"这四个集团中，工人集团由共产党代表说话；知识分子集团由民主党派说话；如果有一个替农民说话的党派，我一定参加。生产资料私人所有制已经消灭了，资产阶级的经济基础已在改变，再强调进步与落后、再强调阶级矛盾，就会影响人民内部的团结。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"735efaf10e"},{"id":"69532b7644","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《右派言论选辑》（河南农学院，1957年12月）。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"735efaf10e"}],"page":{"id":"2c55c65cbe","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"735efaf10e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}